race.comment: BALTIC WAY (1) just missed at Mt Gambier over 1562m first-up in a return to form. He will be fitter and is still well shy of his best. Tumbles in weight with the 4kg claim and can go one better. WHISTLER GIRL (5) was straight back into the winners' circle will over 1800m at Hanging Rock. That stacks right up and she will get every chance racing forward. DRINK THEN KISS (8) is free running and is also going well enough to feature. Missed a nose this trip at Great Western following a comfortable win at Stawell. VIRTUCON (4) just missed at Camperdown over a mile and that also stacks up. Gets back and will come late. REMIGIUS (2) is back on track and is in the mix as well.
